cience</a>.</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"6\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note6a\" data-full-marker=\"6a\">\n<p data-aid=\"128351467\" id=\"note6a_p1\"><span data-note-category=\"tg\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/tg/stewardship?lang=eng\"><small>TG</small> Stewardship</a>.</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"8\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note8a\" data-full-marker=\"8a\">\n<p data-aid=\"128351469\" id=\"note8a_p1\"><span data-note-category=\"cross-ref\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/26.7-10?lang=eng#p8\">3 Ne. 26:8 (7–10)</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/11.22?lang=eng#p22\">D&amp;C 11:22</a>.</span></p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"b\" id=\"note8b\" data-full-marker=\"8b\">\n<p data-aid=\"128351470\" id=\"note8b_p1\"><span data-note-category=\"cross-ref\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/2.27?lang=eng#p27\">2 Ne. 2:27</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/29.12?lang=eng#p12\">29:12</a>.</span></p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"c\" id=\"note8c\" data-full-marker=\"8c\">\n<p data-aid=\"128351472\" id=\"note8c_p1\"><span data-note-category=\"cross-ref\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/90.11?lang=eng#p11\">D&amp;C 90:11</a>.</span></p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"d\" id=\"note8d\" data-full-marker=\"8d\">\n<p data-aid=\"128351474\" id=\"note8d_p1\"><span data-note-category=\"cross-ref\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/alma/12.9-11?lang=eng#p9\">Alma 12:9 (9–11)</a>.</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"9\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note9a\" data-full-marker=\"9a\">\n<p data-aid=\"128351476\" id=\"note9a_p1\"><span data-note-category=\"cross-ref\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/st